            <lg xml:id="TK1020">
<l>nāṇakat tillā riyakka marappāvai</l>
<l>nāṇā luyirmaruṭṭi yaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The actions of those who are without modesty at heart are like those of puppet moved by a string.</l>
